{"tid":1405173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一粒螺絲　累50車爆胎 路政署急召人鋸走","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:14:22.000Z","uid":151324,"like":1269,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8ab3c498578167c06c3d373a725a7fb6d04eeb","tid":1405173,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"2013-12-01<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】一口螺絲成為公路連環殺手！屯門公路往近油柑頭對開路面，昨晨9時起陸續有重型車輛經過時被異物刺穿車胎，多達50輛重型車「中招」，被迫停在路肩等候換胎或拖走，令現場交通擠塞，有36部九巴爆胎，約2.5萬巴士乘客受影響。警方發現是路面一口凸出5厘米的螺絲肇禍，路政署急召承建商到場鋸斷凸起部份，並表示歉意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnwyTRu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnwyTRu.png&h=6cd3f597&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24f7419fc21b8ec83aa6fabac299f92c6a5670e","tid":1405173,"uid":85498,"like":69,"dislike":3,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffd451885f921625bc6e4e4c9ffc5ef8af0ac63","tid":1405173,"uid":642,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5304016b43a95015e9b85f0e5a65a3d390fba8","tid":1405173,"uid":151324,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35313f27a7ee3e7bb77e096901cbc6ec5744c575","tid":1405173,"uid":151324,"like":168,"dislike":3,"score":165,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190101/mobile/bkn-20190101155049612-0101_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190101%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190101155049612-0101_00822_001.html&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=d59cda96\" 