":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258df4e4769dfa4c20eb5951319ed180606f6d6a","tid":1405173,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422a8ca4ec44d96408a1d248d78d11c585178b7e","tid":1405173,"uid":34010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"路政署出招了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"路政署不合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"要fact check <br />\n有巴打渣車佢睇。<br />\n問D工人邊個承建商幫路政。佢地check到螺絲同工程來自一間公司叫誠興，個主席極度藍屍，係廠商會會長咁話。"},{"pid":"f641796fe9b9218fee137c656781ca7a3dd59323","tid":1405173,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好放係警署門口"},{"pid":"92494669037f2925b49aba473698482a26a9655c","tid":1405173,"uid":298009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0e9f3689f462a5dc02fc57ec77299bdd550fb4a","tid":1405173,"uid":298009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258df4e4769dfa4c20eb5951319ed180606f6d6a","tid":1405173,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422a8ca4ec44d96408a1d248d78d11c585178b7e","tid":1405173,"uid":34010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"路政署出招了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"路政署不合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"要fact check <br />\n有巴打渣車佢睇。<br />\n問D工人邊個承建商幫路政。佢地check到螺絲同工程來自一間公司叫誠興，個主席極度藍屍，係廠商會會長咁話。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"HK01<br />\n廠商會會長選舉涉爆誹謗風波 「螺絲大王」徐炳光遭入稟興訴<br />\n撰文：伍凱瑩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZByUQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZByUQ3.jpg&h=1ca714c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廠商會今年底選新會長，兩位副會長吳宏斌和徐炳光有意競逐會長之位，但早前卻爆出傳聞，有會董被指冒名取走選票，這風波最終告上法庭。廠商會副會長史立德及其印刷公司近日入稟高院，控告有「螺絲大王」之稱的徐炳光透過社交媒體散佈誹謗言論，要求法庭頒禁制令和索取賠償。<br />\n徐炳光（左） 揚言角逐會長寶座。（資料圖片）<br />\n史立德指徐炳光在社交媒體發誹謗言論<br />\n原告為史立德及他旗下的華彩印刷有限公司，被告則是徐炳光。入稟狀透露，徐上周四和五透過WhatsApp、WeChat和電郵向廠商會成員和其他非成員散佈針對史立德及其印刷公司的誹謗言論。<br />\n原告要求要求法庭頒禁制令，禁止被告繼續發佈、轉發、刊登或參與有關的誹謗言論，並就誹謗索取賠償。<br />\n【政圈風聲】廠商會改選會長或有三雄爭逐 新會員暴升58%惹關注<br />\n【政圈風聲】廠商會換屆掀搶位戰 梁粉會長接班人遇勁敵<br />\n富二代力挽家業危機 要求父交工廠股權 裁員800炒騙錢親戚<br />\n【法律百科．誹謗】誹謗的定義及主要抗辯理由<br />\n案件編號：HCA2379/2017"},{"pid":"d82f71e4a5910b6590a7b790a6dc098e440dcc46","tid":1405173,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aa3f577e772dc7be45ee344f794cc11d9c44a8","tid":1405173,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【長輩片】</span><br />\n為藍絲長輩而設既Youtube頻道正式面世！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD0RsaWOAv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCD0RsaWOAv4&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=e8e1f911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD0RsaWOAv4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【頻道連結】</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Ffreehongkong&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=d7f912be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝會員「𢭃住中場」（#283968）設立頻道。<br />\n小弟只係幫手宣傳，希幫各位巴絲多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">------------------【原Po】------------------</span></strong><br />\n全靠黑警！終於搵到方法搞掂中立/藍絲屋企人，唔再嘈交！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvwHpT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvwHpT</a></div>"},{"pid":"7dbc32ca81fe58e72b5cc9b6d48614aa37879604","tid":1405173,"uid":91911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d13e7283447a00fa68755fd900d95e299e6758","tid":1405173,"uid":1989,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"4bf5fa970cfa94e788e5f9c6959b75f94a5d438a","tid":1405173,"uid":30510,"like":106,"dislike":3,"score":103,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"用第二招啦<br />\n<br />\n諗下值唔值得啦<br />\n啲車主、運輸公司要用錢好難打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"仲未計好多車主自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到義載都冇車就大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"狗門口放？"},{"pid":"ddbaa643ec41127742560568812f4ea1f36aa8f6","tid":1405173,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9189843c18f320a43ca4de88776a659aede4cefe","tid":1405173,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecfecb63f69001e5563e428ad0803314381279d","tid":1405173,"uid":191366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc5dc9853ae7a0f65295f14406fa13f6eb6f2048","tid":1405173,"uid":23373,"like":219,"dislike":3,"score":216,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"次次都咁講，最後都係平平常常無事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"個個都free rider等人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo